{
  "name": "BERT Encoder",
  "description": "BERT (Google, 2018) — Bidirectional Encoder Representations from Transformers. Pre-trains with Masked Language Modeling (MLM) and Next Sentence Prediction (NSP). The foundation of modern NLU: fine-tune for classification, NER, QA, and more. This example shows BERT-Base (12 layers, 768 dim, 12 heads).",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "dataset-1",
